    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Small creatures, but massive destruction! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/5ba542edb9f872f75b5f929c2fb4bd57.poster.avif?t=1772442756\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/5ba542edb9f872f75b5f929c2fb4bd57.webm?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/5ba542edb9f872f75b5f929c2fb4bd57.mp4?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this colorful <i>survivors-like</i>, summon your trusted allies, the <strong>Chuminis</strong>, to battle hords of forest demons! It’s up to you to manage each Chumini’s <strong>unique behavior</strong> to survive for 20 minutes, and defeat the Dark Druidess. There’re 15 different Chuminis to choose from: find the <strong>best synergies</strong> that suit your playstyle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/79fb16d6e9e2d5c1fddabfce7f7efcad.poster.avif?t=1772442756\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/79fb16d6e9e2d5c1fddabfce7f7efcad.webm?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/79fb16d6e9e2d5c1fddabfce7f7efcad.mp4?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect experience from the defeated demons, build your army of powerful allies and upgrade them to survive! Some Chuminis will run in a circle around you, others will follow your every step… <strong>Optimize your movement to take advantage of your allies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Content</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/f371dd1a9b6554ac774658f727feee01.poster.avif?t=1772442756\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/f371dd1a9b6554ac774658f727feee01.webm?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310000/extras/f371dd1a9b6554ac774658f727feee01.mp4?t=1772442756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 different Chuminis to summon, upgrade, and use in battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An &quot;ability&quot; system tied to each Chumini</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 unique enemies and 2 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful hand-drawn graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A meta-progression system offering replayability and difficulty levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements to collect!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What you WONT find in our Survivors-like (for now):</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different maps or levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different playable characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not expect endless replayabity through unlock</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
